---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { STORM_DOOR_URL } from '../consts';
---
<Base
  title="The Sound of Something More — Jonathan Sexton"
  description="The book Jonathan Sexton is writing under the mentorship of Kathryn Aalto. Songs belong on a shelf with dreams and prayers, the things we believe in but cannot prove."
  nav="solid"
>
  <div class="pagehead">
    <p class="kicker">What I'm writing</p>
    <h1>The Sound of Something More</h1>
    <p class="standfirst">Songs belong on a shelf with dreams and prayers. The things we believe in but cannot measure or prove.</p>
  </div>

  <article class="read">
    <div class="col reveal">
      <p class="lede">We accept that a dream can change a life. We accept that a prayer can reach somewhere words can't. We have forgotten that a song does the same work, and that we always knew it did.</p>

      <p>The Sound of Something More is a book about that forgetting, and about remembering in time. It uses music as the lens for how to stay human while the machines get faster. It reaches back into the archives, the Library of Congress, the Parchman recordings, the old ballad about the man who beat the steam drill, and it lands on the question the bridge generation is the last to be able to answer, having grown up analog and gone to work digital.</p>

      <span class="kicker">The shape of it</span>
      <p>It opens close to home, in a Tennessee living room, and widens into the history without ever crossing a line the reader can feel. The personal is evidence, not the subject. The mode is inquiry. The voice is the one you'll find in The Storm Door most Saturdays.</p>

      <blockquote>You already know. Stop pretending you don't.</blockquote>

      <span class="kicker">Where it stands</span>
      <p>The manuscript is most of the way there, written under two years of mentorship from New York Times bestselling author Kathryn Aalto. There's no cover to show yet and no date to hold you to. When there is, you'll hear it first through the letter.</p>

      <p style="margin-top:1.8rem">
        <a class="btn" href={STORM_DOOR_URL} rel="noopener" style="text-decoration:none;color:#f6f2ea">Follow along in The Storm Door <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </p>

      <p class="note">The Sound of Something More is a work in progress. Pages and excerpts will appear here as they're ready to be read.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
